# Planning Mode Guidelines

**When to Use Planning Mode:**
- Tasks with 3+ distinct steps
- Complex features requiring multiple files
- Integration work across modules
- Refactoring that affects multiple components

**Planning Process:**
1. Reference @docs/architecture/system-overview.md in plans
2. Break down complex features into actionable todos
3. Validate plans against existing patterns before execution
